.. _smb-posit:

SMB Positions
---------------

The holdings are as of end of September. The table on the left shows the stocks in the top 50% cutoff of ME, depicted by
positive (long) holdings and the table on the right shows the bottom 50% cutoff of ME, depicted by negative (short) holdings

Check out our :ref:`hml-posit` and :ref:`wml-posit`
